    <svcsubproc>
        <title>External Block Heater Connection</title>
        <para>The optional block heater receptacle is located in the lower center portion of the bumper opening. It is
            mounted on a bracket and bolted to the lower bumper opening flange.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To remove the receptacle, unplug the connection at the rear of the heater receptacle. Push
                in on plug connection to release lock and pull plug out to remove.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate and remove the lower mounting bolts on the bumper flange.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the receptacle.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Follow the reverse procedure to install.</para>
        </step1>
